Detailed Description

An BonusFile like it appears in the server-side XML file.

This structur defines an entry in the tBonusFileList, which is used by the xmlBonusFileList class. I defines a BonusFile header, not its content.

To have the content of a BonusFile, see xmlBonusFile.
